TITLE: Integrating Custom Property Update into Logging Logic (Function Command, JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Modified `logCRMEvent` function for a function command. Instead of directly completing the event after successfully getting the body, it now calls `updateCustomProperties` to set the 'EventLogged' flag. The completion signal (`event.completed`) is subsequently handled within `updateCustomProperties` upon successful saving of the property.
SOURCE: https://github.com/officedev/office-js-docs-pr/blob/main/docs/outlook/mobile-log-appointments.md#_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: js
