TITLE: Loading and Enumerating All Shape Bindings - PowerPoint Office JS - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates loading all bindings from the PowerPoint bindings collection and logging their IDs to the console. The function uses the load method to prepare binding data, context.sync to fetch, and iterates over each binding to output its identifier. Optional error handling is included for API failures.
