TITLE: Implementing OBO Token Exchange with MSAL in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Implements the core On-Behalf-Of (OBO) flow logic within the route handler. It extracts the assertion token from the Authorization header, defines the required scopes (`files.read`), validates the necessary `access_as_user` scope, and uses `authHelper.getConfidentialClientApplication().acquireTokenOnBehalfOf()` to exchange the assertion for a Microsoft Graph access token. Includes placeholders for Graph API call (`TODO 11`) and error handling (`TODO 12`). Requires the 'jsonwebtoken' library (`jwt`) and the configured `authHelper`.
