TITLE: Complete toggleProtection Handler with Async Loading and Toggling (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Provides the final implementation of toggleProtection handler: queues worksheet property loading, syncs, checks protection status, toggles protection, syncs updates, and completes the Office action. Error handling is included to capture exceptions. Dependencies: Office.js and registered handler mapping in manifest.
