TITLE: Configuring Web API Routing in ASP.NET (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This C# snippet configures Web API routing for an ASP.NET project by mapping attribute-based and default HTTP routes. It must reside in the WebApiConfig.cs file within an App_Start folder. Key parameters are the route template for API controllers and optional id. This setup is a prerequisite for enabling Web API endpoints in the solution.
