TITLE: Configuring XML Manifest for No Item Context Activation in Outlook
DESCRIPTION: This XML snippet replaces the entire '<VersionOverrides>' section in an Outlook add-in's 'manifest.xml' file. It specifies the Mailbox requirement set 1.13, defines a 'MessageReadCommandSurface' extension point with a button control ('msgReadOpenPaneButton') that triggers a 'ShowTaskpane' action. Crucially, it includes the '<SupportsNoItemContext>true</SupportsNoItemContext>' element within the '<Action>' element, enabling the add-in to activate without the Reading Pane enabled or a message selected. It also defines necessary resources like icons and URLs.
