TITLE: Closing the File Connection using closeAsync (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Defines the `closeFile` function which is called after all slices have been sent. It uses the `File.closeAsync` method from the Office JavaScript API to close the connection to the document file and release associated resources. It updates the status message based on the success or failure of the asynchronous close operation.
