DESCRIPTION: This code defines a constant string representing the SOAP request XML needed to execute a GetAttachment operation against Exchange Web Services (EWS). The string is formatted to insert an attachment ID at runtime using String.Format, enabling dynamic requests for specific attachment resources. The XML includes necessary namespaces and structure for EWS, and is designed to be injected into an HTTP POST body during the web service call.
