SOURCE: https://github.com/officedev/office-js-docs-pr/blob/main/docs/excel/excel-add-ins-worksheets.md#_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// This method clears the AutoFilter setting from one column.
await Excel.run(async (context) => {
    // Retrieve the active worksheet.
    let sheet = context.workbook.worksheets.getActiveWorksheet();

    // Clear the filter from only column 3.
    sheet.autoFilter.clearColumnCriteria(3);
    await context.sync();
});
```

