LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
$.ajax({\n    type: \"POST\",\n    url: \"/api/DoSomething\",\n    headers: {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer \" + accessToken\n    },\n    data: { /* some JSON payload */ },\n    contentType: \"application/json; charset=utf-8\"\n}).done(function (data) {\n    // Handle success\n}).fail(function (error) {\n    // Handle error\n}).always(function () {\n    // Cleanup\n});
```

