TITLE: Taskpane Body Markup for SSO User Info Display (HTML)
DESCRIPTION: This HTML snippet defines a simple UI for the Office Add-in task pane, including a 'Get ID Token' button and a container to display retrieved user info. This markup is used both in Visual Studio and Yo Office projects to provide a clear interface for users to initiate token retrieval and view SSO results. The button and span elements are referenced from JavaScript logic for interactivity.
